The French option had been an insurance policy should the ground become too quick at Doncaster but Kingston Hill now looks certain to run in the Leger.

Dettori’s mount Forever Now has been regarded as a long-term Leger project by four-time winner Gosden, who teamed up with Dettori to win the Classic with Shantou in 1996.

Dettori, jocked off Arc favourite Treve on Monday before being beaten on £5.25million Naamah 24 hours later, said: ‘I don’t

